      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\">A medical student is reviewing infectious disease terminology in preparation for his exams. He comes across a term that describes a pathogen&#39;s capacity to cause noticeable illness in a host. Which of the following terms best defines this concept?</span></p>",
